{"lastModified":1776326390065,"uri":"c::10819594065::vessel::9928a930-201b-11f0-a24c-e5a2f59a88ff","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Operating Area: Italy\n\nStep aboard the Riva 88’ Folgore “ALLORA”, a yacht that embodies power, elegance,\nand cutting-edge technology. Designed to turn heads and deliver maximum comfort,\nthe 88’ Folgore is your gateway to the most exclusive destinations in style.\n\nSmooth Sailing – Comfort Without Compromise\nWorried about seasickness? No need. The 88’ Folgore is equipped with state-of-theart stabilizers, ensuring a smooth and steady ride even when side waves hit.Whether cruising at high speed or at anchor, enjoy the journey without motion discomfort, making your experience effortless and enjoyable.\n\nPerfect Outdoor Comfort\nDesigned for all-day relaxation, the flybridge and aft deck offer shade protection, allowing you to soak in the breathtaking views while staying cool and comfortable. Whether lounging in the spacious outdoor seating areas or basking in the sun on the generous sundeck, every detail is crafted for your pleasure.\n\nYour Exclusive Escape\nDesigned for those who seek the ultimate yachting experience, the Riva 88’ Folgore offers luxury, stability, and timeless beauty—all in one extraordinary vessel.","blueprint":{"name":"ALLORA","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::9928a930-201b-11f0-a24c-e5a2f59a88ff::assets::088c8ff0-201f-11f0-b090-37c711c639e2/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::10819594065::vessel::9928a930-201b-11f0-a24c-e5a2f59a88ff::assets::b82c7b00-0b2e-11f1-8d1e-b393be503c53/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::10819594065::vessel::9928a930-201b-11f0-a24c-e5a2f59a88ff::assets::b82b1b70-0b2e-11f1-8d1c-b393be503c53/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::10819594065::vessel::9928a930-201b-11f0-a24c-e5a2f59a88ff::assets::b82c05d0-0b2e-11f1-8d1d-b393be503c53/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::10819594065::vessel::9928a930-201b-11f0-a24c-e5a2f59a88ff::assets::b82cf030-0b2e-11f1-8d1e-b3